    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于这款游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑白之地是一款能带给你街机般快节奏体验的，多人弹幕射击游戏，在持久的BOSS战中，积累经验获取装备，和其他玩家一起并肩作战，战胜BOSS！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/59ab2593c96dc53f44947a00abdf992a.poster.avif?t=1754119927\" width=698 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/59ab2593c96dc53f44947a00abdf992a.webm?t=1754119927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/59ab2593c96dc53f44947a00abdf992a.mp4?t=1754119927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >街机式的游戏体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快节奏的游戏体验，随时进入游戏随时退出，简单上手但极具挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将和其他玩家一起，面对拥有独特战斗方式的几百种BOSS和精英怪物，击败它们，搜刮传奇战利品，或者被它们击败...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/f58e5f7c07b1dd8a33a79373ff8fbe40.poster.avif?t=1754119927\" width=666 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/f58e5f7c07b1dd8a33a79373ff8fbe40.webm?t=1754119927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/f58e5f7c07b1dd8a33a79373ff8fbe40.mp4?t=1754119927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化的养成和跨平台的体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的英雄们会伴随着你一起成长，他们的死亡会让你更加强大，多达百种装备的专精以及丰富的技能，遗物，天赋，随行兽，可以组成不同的build。我们甚至希望PC玩家可以和移动端玩家一起进行游戏，感受这种跨平台的游戏体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/46ac3bc9a1bc18d274961fcbb546d2fa.poster.avif?t=1754119927\" width=664 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/46ac3bc9a1bc18d274961fcbb546d2fa.webm?t=1754119927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/46ac3bc9a1bc18d274961fcbb546d2fa.mp4?t=1754119927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >付费模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在的付费设计主要是会员和通行证，你可以通过这些解锁一些便捷功能，或者额外的外观。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/24f664e359df025c93045e061aeb1602.poster.avif?t=1754119927\" width=666 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/24f664e359df025c93045e061aeb1602.webm?t=1754119927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2258890/extras/24f664e359df025c93045e061aeb1602.mp4?t=1754119927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关注我们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入QQ群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >778583793</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >764397132</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >740105815</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KOOK「黑白之地」官方社区 : 23435442</p>",
